                <td class="px-5 py-3 align-top">The broader discipline of optimising brand content and entity signals to achieve visibility across all AI-driven search surfaces. GEO encompasses AEO and extends to LLM citation strategy, entity authority building, and cross-platform AI visibility measurement.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--line-soft)]">
                <td class="px-5 py-3 font-medium text-ink-100 align-top">Search Engine Optimisation</td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3 align-top font-mono text-xs text-[var(--accent)]">SEO</td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3 align-top">The practice of optimising web content to rank highly in organic search results on search engines such as Google and Bing. SEO targets position within a ranked list; AEO targets selection as the answer. Both are required for comprehensive search visibility.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--line-soft)]">
