                <td class="px-5 py-3 align-top">A box displayed above Google's organic results ("position zero") that extracts a passage, list, or table from a single web page and presents it as the direct answer to a query. The primary AEO target on Google Search. Three formats: paragraph, list, and table snippets.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--line-soft)]">
